author: desruisseaux
msg: Begin reorganization of developer guide. The plan is to split the guide in smaller documents in a "book" directory (the source files),
and assemble them in the target "developer-guide.html" file by a Java command-line to be provided in the 'sis-build-helper' module.
That Java command-line would also select automatically the CSS class of <code> and <pre> elements, thus simplifying considerably the
code snippets. It would also generate the table of content.
